column2: SELECT s.apogee_id, s.ra, s.dec, s.vhelio_avg, s.vscatter, s.survey, s.snr,    params.*, paramerrs.*, elems.*, elemerrs.*,   dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlagN(a.aspcapflag),   dbo.fApogeeStarFlagN(s.starflag) FROM apogeeStar s   JOIN aspcapStar a on a.apstar_id = s.apstar_id   CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParams(a.aspcap_id) params   CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParamErrs(a.aspcap_id) paramerrs   CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapElems(a.aspcap_id) elems   CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapElemErrs(a.aspcap_id) elemerrs WHERE s.apogee_id = &&&   OR  s.apogee_id = &&&   OR  s.apogee_id = &&&   OR  s.apogee_id = &&& INTO mydb.rgeb
